---
title: Double Southeast Asian Chicken & Garlic Rice with Honey-Soy Veggies & Japanese Mayo
description: Look out for the king of seasonings, Southeast Asian spice blend! With all the spicy flavour, pan-fried onto juicy
chicken, this is a quick and easy dinner that's going to blow your mind.

*We’ve replaced the crispy shallots in this recipe with spring onion due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just
as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
